||= [[span class="metam"]]**__METAME**__[[/span]]**RAISA**[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]**Previously** Anomalous Communications, Extradimensional Anomalies, Extrasolar Activities, Interdimensional Stability, Ontokinetics, 'Pataphysical Cosmology, Paraastronomy, and Parabiology & Rhizospherics.[[/span]][[span class="metam"]]**__METICS__**[[/span]]||= Biological Research & Specialized Containment Area-12||
||~ PROJECT LEAD ||~ RESEARCH HEAD ||
||= **N/A** ||= Dr. Quentin T. Toth, //Humanoid & Esoteric Research//. ||
[[/div]]

[[div class="modal" style="font-size: 92%;"]]
[[span class="st"]]__SPECIAL CONTAINMENT PROCEDURES:__[[/span]] All entrances to [[span class="st"]]ITER-Î¨[[/span]] are currently inaccessible to civilian or state entities.

Aperture-Î©2 (APT-Î©2), and by extension Aperture-Î©1 (APT-Î©1), are contained within a standard hard-vacuum graviton-containment chamber in [*/secure-facility-dossier-area-12 Biological Research Area-12]'s Humanoid & Esoteric Containment Wing Theta within the Anomaly Operations Sector. In case of a temporary graviton containment failure, the chamber frame has been reinforced with a titanium alloy to ensure structural integrity through any potential gravitational disturbances and has been fitted with a thick layer of Niobium C-103 to withstand and contain the internal vacuum conditions, along with the immense thermal radiation that is continuously propagated through the apertures. The containment unit is accessible through an airlock only traversable by individuals equipped with specialized extreme-heat-resistant pressure suits, access is exclusively permitted with approval from the object's Research Head.
[[/div]]

[[include component:image-block
name=https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-7555/Anomaly.png
|caption=Î± Canis Majoris -- as viewed through a heavily underexposed image of APT-Î©1 & APT-Î©2.
|width=100%
|align=center]]

[[div class="modal" style="font-size: 92%;"]]
[[span class="st"]]__DESCRIPTION:__[[/span]] [[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]] refers to a titanic biological mass contained within an extrauniversal space designated "[[span class="st"]]ITER-Î¨[[/span]]", the exact dimensions of both are unknown. The object is a sentient, biovorous, heterotrophic, spatiokinetic[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]**spatiokinesis:** a sub-category of ontokinesis describing the ability of an anomaly to manipulate the spatial dimensions of matter.[[/span]] organism composed of several anomalous segments visually resembling that of the mammalian digestive tract:

[[include :scp-wiki:component:image-features-source |click-fullscreen=--]
|speed=500
|float=true
|align=right
|width=350px
|url=https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-7555/Diagram1.png
|add-caption=true
|caption=Visual diagram of inter- and intra-universal travel between our universe //(**Î©**)// and [[span class="st"]]ITER-Î¨[[/span]] //(**Î¨**)//
]]

* **EQUIVALENT ORAL CAVITIES:** APT-Î©1 & -Î©2, two apertures of an otherwise non-anomalous Morrisâ€“Thorne Class-A Traversable Wormhole, will trigger an anomalous property when biological material attempts to traverse through one aperture and out the other. Instead of being transported through to the other side, the material is instead transferred into [[span class="st"]]ITER-Î¨[[/span]] via a third aperture, designated "WAY-Î¨0".

* **EQUIVALENT ESOPHAGI:** Biological materials now within [[span class="st"]]ITER-Î¨[[/span]] are drawn into one of many large esophagi, all inconsistent in size, shape, and appearance, where they are now transported further into [[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]].[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]Current observations suggest [[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]]'s stomachs may attract matter through their respective esophagi with a gravitational field which is only exerted upon 3-dimensional biological materials.[[/span]]

* **EQUIVALENT STOMACHS:** 3-dimensional materials within the stomach now undergo a process of dimensional adoption, a newly discovered anomalous process where dimensionally stable material will begin to adopt an additional spatial dimension. In contrast to typical dimensional shedding,[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]**dimensional shedding:** a primarily anomalous process where material with //n//-spatial dimensions abruptly begins to degenerate in stability, the matter is then forced to "shed" a spatial dimension as to not collapse in upon itself and be subsequently annihilated into disparate elementary particles.[[/span]] which is an independent process, dimensional adoption has only been observed to occur within [[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]] and is thereby believed to be dependent upon its specific anomalous mechanisms.

* **EQUIVALENT INTESTINES:** The internals of [[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]] past its stomachs remain unexplored, non-biological materials appear entirely incapable of passing through the equivalent duodenum.[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]The first section of the small intestine.[[/span]]

It is unknown whether this dimensional "digestive" process serves to provide [[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]] with any form of physiological benefit, as the induced adoption of an additional spatial dimension in matter would suggest otherwise; expending energy and providing it additional mass throughout the process.

The Morrisâ€“Thorne Class-A Traversable Wormhole that forms [[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]]'s oral cavities bridge and allow for non-biological material to traverse between two (2) locations[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]Within our universe.[[/span]] through their respective apertures. One end located in a specialized vacuum containment chamber within Area-12's Humanoid & Esoteric Containment Wing Theta (APT-Î©1), and the other located in close orbit of Sirius B, a main-sequence Type-A star located in the nearby Orion constellation (APT-Î©2). These connect to each other through conventional means, conforming to standard, non-anomalous cosmological models. Their anomalous attributes manifest only when biological material attempts to pass through either aperture, redirecting the material through a third, inter-universal Way, designated WAY-Î¨0.

[[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]] is highly intelligent and capable of advanced communication with Foundation researchers through manipulation of exotic matter[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]A type of matter with negative mass (e.g. -1kg).[[/span]] within its aperture, causing highly directed localized gravitational disturbances towards nearby structures -- resulting vibrations can then be picked up through seismographs and translated through Morse code. [[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]] appears to be able to discern vibrations in its nearby vicinity despite the surrounding vacuum within its containment chamber, further research into this ability is ongoing.

The parasite-universe, designated "[[span class="st"]]ITER-Î¨[[/span]]", is connected to -- and completely dependent upon -- our own universe. The dimensional condition of [[span class="st"]]ITER-Î¨[[/span]] oscillates irregularly between three (3) and four (4) spatial dimensions, often simultaneously displaying attributes of both; --believed to be remnant of its primordial formation conditions and subsequent dependence upon our universe's reality--. It is theorized that this //m///3.5/1-space[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]**SPATIOTEMPORAL DIMENSIONS:** 3.5 spatial and 1 temporal dimension, for a total of 4.5 spatiotemporal (space-time) dimensions.[[/span]]|[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]**NARRATIVE DIMENSIONS:** The narrative dimensions of [[span class="st"]]ITER-Î¨[[/span]] (//m//) have yet to be successfully measured. This is in large part due to narrative cosmological studies' state as an extremely young parascience; only recently proposed and partially verified by [*/scp-5242 Dr. Place H. McDoctorate] -- still largely esoteric to the majority of Foundation researchers.[[/span]] formed with 4 spatial dimensions --and is attempting to adopt conditions similar to that of its new host--.

How or why this universe formed remains unknown. Adverse universal hume conditions have been ruled out as a potential cause, with current theories suggesting the more likely possibility that natural, extra-universal forces beyond biological human conception were either partially or wholly at play. However, with what limited information has been gathered to date, the resting narrative energy within [[span class="st"]]ITER-Î¨[[/span]] is believed to be in a state of degenerative metastability.[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]The potential consequences of a hypothetical false narrative decay event and the subsequent narrative bubble nucleation would, by definition, elude human conception.[[/span]] 

Unless specified otherwise APT-Î©1 & -Î©2 will from here on out be included in reference to "[[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]]".
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="notation" style="max-width: 70%; font-size: 92%;"]]
= [[span class="st"]]__ADDENDUM ERR.I:__[[/span]] Discovery
----
[[div class="blockquote"]]
[[==]]
[[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]] was discovered on 25/06/2020 when the Composite Orbital Early Warning System (COEWS) reported anomalous graviton and photon fluctuations within High Earth Orbit. Traveling at approximately 29.78 km/s, the object was marked by automated systems as a likely K-Class meteoroid[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]**K-Class**: a catch-all term for objects, anomalous or otherwise, that present a potential hazard to a majority of human life.[[/span]] with significant anomalous attributes on a twenty (20) minute impact course with the Eastern United States. Conventional ground-to-orbit weapons installations proved entirely incapable of acquiring a successful target lock on the object. And the order to utilize anomalous alternatives was canceled when it was calculated that sufficiently powerful installations would be incapable of spooling up in time to avert the impact.

The dire state of affairs necessitated an external call to aid. The Global Occult Coalition was contacted and informed of the unfolding incident and was provided clearance to liquidate the object despite its presence within mutually agreed-upon SCPF territory. Five (5) minutes later a launch was detected from the YucatÃ¡n Peninsula, Mexico, with the projectile accelerating to an estimated 18.532% the speed of light before reaching the approximate location of [[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]], disappearing from scopes precisely 00:01:22 before the object's impact with Earth.

[[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]] appeared entirely unaffected by the launch, continuing on its calculated trajectory towards the Eastern United States.

= //<Further neutralization attempts omitted.>//

[[include component:image-block
name=https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-7555/path.jpg
|caption=Path left in [[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]]'s wake.
|width=320px
|align=left]]

[[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]] landed on the outskirts of the village of Bemis, West Virginia. Upon discerning the lack of an impact event, the nearest available Mobile Task Force was rapidly mobilized and deployed to the area.

[[div class="floatbox right metam"]]
= **NOTE:**

= Possession ensured.
[[/div]]

MTF Zeta-19 (â€œLonely Onlyâ€) arrived in the remote village fifteen (15) minutes later; finding no signs of life or human activity. After clearing each building within the village the team discovered [[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]] within the local church, screaming having been noted from within mere moments before entry was made. The entity was found behind the church altar, generating significant gravitational disturbances. The team utilized Local Gravitic ("LoGrav") Priority Devices[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]A biomechanical device constructed from instances of [[[SCP-1136]]].[[/span]] to safely approach the aperture and deploy a High Ultimate Tensile Strength ("HUTS") carbon-nanotube provisional containment system around the entity, successfully encasing it.

[[div class="floatbox right metam"]]
= **NOTE:**

= Insufficient.
[[/div]]

Containment teams arrived shortly after and took the object into custody, [[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]] was securely transported to the nearest containment facility for evaluation and processing --  Area-12 was chosen as the prime candidate and the object was temporarily assigned to the facility's Humanoid & Esoteric Division. Additional sweeps of the village and surrounding area are carried out; no human activity is noted.
[[/==]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="jailers_memo"]]
The Global Occult Coalition was not informed of the true nature of the incident. The Jointâ€Œ â€ŒAmbassadorsâ€Œ â€Œinâ€Œ â€ŒLesseningâ€Œ â€ŒExternalâ€Œ â€ŒRelationsâ€Œ â€ŒStressesâ€Œ will continue to ensure their belief that despite [[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]]'s successful impact with Earth's surface, no significant damage resulted largely due to a successful liquidation of the vast majority of the object's mass upon contact with the projectile launched from the YucatÃ¡n Peninsula.

All requests for samples or records of the non-existent remains of the impact have been summarily denied or ignored.
[[/div]]

= [[span class="st"]]END ADDENDUM[[/span]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

