= [[span class="st"]]__ADDENDUM ERR.II:__[[/span]] Anomaly Communication

[[table]]
[[row]]
[[hcell]]
AUTOMATED VIDEO TRANSCRIPT
[[/hcell]]
[[/row]]
[[row]]
[[cell]]
**DATE:** 30/06/2020

**TRANSCRIBER:** Crius.aic

**PARTIES PRESENT:**

* Asst. Director of Research Dr. Quentin T. Toth
* Anomalous Communications Expert Prof. BjÃ¶rn Ã…. Lundkvist
* [[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]]

**[.AIC] FOREWORD:** Following the detection of clear Morse code patterns in [[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]]'s gravitational waves, Area-12 Anomalous Communications Expert Prof. BjÃ¶rn Ã…. Lundkvist was requested by Anomaly Head Researcher Dr. Quentin T. Toth to assist in establishing communications.

[[/cell]]
[[/row]]
[[row]]
[[hcell]]
Â«BEGIN TRANSCRIPTÂ»
[[/hcell]]
[[/row]]
[[row]]
[[hcell]]

[[div class="blockquote"]]
##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## All done?

##FFD300|**Prof. Lundkvist:**## All done. Just -- start it simple. You never know with these things, so swallow all that Ph.D. Ivy-league talk of yours.

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## //I know//, I know. Thank you.

//<Dr. Toth kisses Prof. Lundkvist on the forehead and sits down beside him. Lundkvist chuckles.>//

##FFD300|**Prof. Lundkvist:**## I thought interpersonal displays of affection were against behavioral guidelines, this is all on video you know.

//<Dr. Toth giggles and gives a dismissive hand-wave.>//

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## Such a stupid policy. If HR has a problem Mondithoka can take it up with me herself, I outrank everyone in that department anyway. //<Dr. Toth looks down at her wristwatch.>// Ah -- let's get this show on the road, shall we?

//<Translation equipment boot-time omitted for brevity.>//

[[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]]**:** --[[span class="quint"]]SSENCE[[/span]]

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## Finally.

//<Dr. Toth leans into the microphone>//

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## Hello. Can you understand us?

[[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]]**:** [[span class="quint"]]YES -- IT HAS BEEN LONG -- WHO AM I SPEAKING TO?[[/span]]

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## Doctor Quentin Toth and Professor BjÃ¶rn Lundkvist. We speak to you on behalf of the SCP Foundation.

[[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]]**:** [[span class="quint"]]NICE TO MEET YOU BOTH -- I LIKE YOUR NAMES.[[/span]]

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## Thank you, do you have one yourself?

[[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]]**:** [[span class="quint"]]NEVER ASSIGNED -- DIFFICULT TO REMEMBER.[[/span]]

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## I'm sorry to hear that, may I ask where you originate from then?

[[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]]**:** [[span class="quint"]]HERE.[[/span]]

//<Pause -- Dr. Toth looks over toward Prof. Lundkvist for a brief moment before returning to the microphone.>//

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## "Here?" Are you claiming you were born in this containment cell?

[[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]]**:** [[span class="quint"]]I CAME INTO BEING WITHIN THE WARM EMBRACE OF THIS STAR.[[/span]]

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## Ah. Are you referring to our star or Sirius? The one seen through //...// you.

[[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]]**:** [[span class="quint"]]THE STARS DO NOT BELONG TO YOU.[[/span]]

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## I -- yes. Apologies, I misspoke. We'll get back to that. //Let's move on to why we're here anyway// --

//<Prof. Lundkvist mutes the microphone.>//

##FFD300|**Prof. Lundkvist:**## You need to establish a rapport bef --

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## Oh please, BjÃ¶rn.

##FFD300|**Prof. Lundkvist:**## We ca --

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## Executive decision. I really don't have time for this. Noospherics has-

##FFD300|**Prof. Lundkvist:**## "No-uh-spherics". Not "Noo-spherics". NoÃ¶spherics. There's an umlaut on the second "O" to delineate the correct pronunciation.

//<Silence.>//

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## //NoÃ¶spherics// has demanded my presence and wants me topside in half an hour for a lift to some last-minute emergency summit for my input on ... I don't know, they didn't tell me. So let's get this done -- and done fast.

//<Silence.>//

##FFD300|**Prof. Lundkvist:**## Not in the mood today, huh?

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## Not particularly, no.

##FFD300|**Prof. Lundkvist:**## //Ã„lskling//, this is not a rush job. You know that.

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## //BjÃ¶rn.//

##FFD300|**Prof. Lundkvist:**## //<Sigh>// Just -- don't antagonize it, please?

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**##//<Pause.>// Sorry.

//<Dr. Toth unmutes the microphone.>//

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## Hello? Still there?

[[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]]**:** [[span class="quint"]]EVERYWHERE.[[/span]]

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## Okay. We need you to tell us what happened to the inhabitants of Bemis village.

[[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]]**:** [[span class="quint"]]BEMIS?[[/span]]

##5DB3B2|**Dr. Toth:**## Forgotten already? That's where you emptied an entire town full of people.

[[span class="bt"]]OBJECT 5[[/span]]**:** [[span class="quint"]]I -- SEE.[[/span]]

